        .hero-unit.hero-background.hidden#faq-content
          .question Why are we doing this?
          .answer Other than the fact that we love Holly?  Maybe you don't know her so you don't love her yet but you will.  Take a look at the video if you need another reason.
          .question Why do I have to pledge first and then complete a paypal request?
          .answer Paypal charges 2.9% + .30 for every donation if you were to make it directly on this site.  However if you pledge an ammount I can send you a paypal request for that amount and we can skip the fees.  This will allow us to raise our goal much faster.
          .question What if we raise the money and she still can't make it for some reason?
          .answer We really hope that this isn't the case but if there is some unforseen issue and Holly can't make it we do have a plan.  First of all we are going to buy the tickets first and if we need to we can sell them and get everyone paid back.  The rest of the money will be paid back to donors in cash.
          .question How do I know my donation has been counted?
          .answer There is a real time donation tracker on the home page.  Once you make your donation you can see the total increase.
          .question Is there any other way to donate?
          .answer Sure there are lots of ways.  You can walk right up to Holly and hand her cash if you wish but for the purposes of this site paypal is the only way.
          .question What if I can't afford to pitch in but I still want to help?
          .answer You can spread the word on this site and / or leave encouraging words for those who have donated on the comment section.
